The '''Corellian Space Museum''' was located in [[Coronet City/Legends|Coronet City]], [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. It was filled with artifacts from the earliest history of space flight such as the original [[Corellian Treaty (25,000 BBY)|Corellian Treaty]].<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

